channel.title: [614] Item On Interface
channel.description:
Hey, I've recently switched from coding a 562 to coding a 614.. The 562 server had an option to send an item on an interface (the method was called "itemOnInterface"). It had a specific ID, but that ID changed for the 614.. So does anyone know the new ID for this packet? I've tried to figure it out, but I'm having no luck :/.
EDIT: If no one knows the actual ID, could anyone give me some tips in finding the new ID?
